<p><b>NOTE:</b> The <b>2016</b> <a href="/racewalking/team_championships"><b>IAAF World Race Walking Team Championships</b></a> was the 27th edition of the global team racewalking competition organized by the International Association of Athletics Federations. It was held in Rome, Italy from 7 to 8 May 2016. It was the first edition of the tournament under its new name, having previously been known as the <a href="/racewalking/worldcup"><b>IAAF World Race Walking Cup</b></a> since 1989.</p>